review_data: Reviewed in the United States on July 30, 2021
name: Stella Carrier
title: Good Mix of Three Fruits Flavor
review: This 4 pack of GoGo Squeez Happy Tummiez apple banana strawberry 3.2 oz pouches (4 pack) have the ideal mix of pleasantly sweet apple banana and strawberry taste. I enjoy that this snack has also a hybrid texture flavor of a smoothie and applesauce mixed together. I feel that the taste is enhanced when the pouches are refrigerated, however these pouches also still taste good at room temperature.
